Basic Installation
==================

# Required are for building are:
# - libtoolize (from package libtool)
# - libdatrie (https://github.com/tlwg/libdatrie or package libdatrie1)

# When downloaded from the Github repo (Skip for released tarballs)
./autogen.sh

./configure
# Or to install elsewhere: ./configure --prefix=...

make

# Recommended
make check

# With elevated permissions if required
make install

# In order to uninstall
make uninstall

